                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "《原神》纪念PV-「荧荧微光」",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/07/142453215/2cba4dd4430184104782640ed1f77225_7289708540827647480.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "2022年9月17日",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "「或许只有当深渊般的黑夜降临，才能注意到一直陪伴身旁的荧荧微光。」",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube：",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
